             Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
             Lt*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                 t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) + 
             Lt*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
                 t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
               t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*
                Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
                 t]) - Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*
              (-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                 t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
             (mm*(2*Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                    t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
                2*Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                    Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][
                     mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
             (mb*(2*Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*
                    Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][
                     bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
                  Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][mla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][
                     t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
                  Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2))) + 
        (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
         (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
            (-(Fbly*Ls*Cos[bla[t]]) - kml*(-mA + Pi - bla[t] + mla[t]) - 
             Fblx*Ls*Sin[bla[t]] + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*
              Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*
              Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + Ls*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][
               t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                 t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
             Ls*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
                 t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][mra][t]) - (mb*(2*Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bla][t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][
                     t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
                  Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][
                     t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
                  Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2)) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(Fbly*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] + Fmly*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] + 
            Fty*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] - kt*(Pi - tA - mla[t] - mra[t]) + 
            kmr*(-mA + Pi - bra[t] + mra[t]) - Fblx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] - 
            Fmlx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] - Ftx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Lt*mt*Sin[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] + 
              Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Sin[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
              Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
              t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
              Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
              Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
              Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
              t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - 
              Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
            (mt*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][bra][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
                   t]) - 2*Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
                (-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
            (mm*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                   t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*
                Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                   t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
            (mb*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
                (-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                   t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*
                Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
                   t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2)))))/
    (Lt*(mb + mm)*mt*(Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]] - Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
     (Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bra[t]] - Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
     (Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
     (-((-((-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
                Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*
                Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
               Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])) + 
            (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + 
              Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]^2))*
           (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*
                Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*
                Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
              (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
                Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
              Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[
                bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
              Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]]))) + (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*
               Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^
                2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
             (Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mla[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[
                mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]]))*(-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
              Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[
                mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
             (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])))*(((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]) - 
           (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*
            (Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
          (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[
                mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[
                bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + 
              Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
           (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
             Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) - 
         ((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]) - (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]))*
          (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[
                bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
              Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
           (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2)))) + 
      (-(((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]) - (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]))*
          (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 
              Ls^2*mt*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + 
              2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
             (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))) + 
        ((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])^2 - (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*
           (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 
            Ls^2*mt*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + 
            2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2))*
         (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])))*
       ((-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
         (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
            Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*
           (-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
            Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) - 
        (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]^2))*
         (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
            Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2))))), 
  -((kml*Ls*mA*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - kml*Ls*mb*Pi*Cos[bla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]] + kt*Ls*mb*Pi*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - 
      kt*Ls*mb*tA*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + kml*Ls*mb*bla[t]*Cos[bla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]] + kml*Lt*mA*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
      kml*Lt*mA*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - kml*Lt*mb*Pi*Cos[mla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]] - kml*Lt*mm*Pi*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
      kml*Lt*mb*bla[t]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + kml*Lt*mm*bla[t]*Cos[mla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]] + Fmly*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - 
      Fbly*Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - 
      kml*Ls*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*mla[t] - kt*Ls*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]*mla[t] - kml*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*mla[t] - 
      kml*Lt*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*mla[t] - kt*Ls*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]*mra[t] - Fblx*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*
       Sin[bla[t]] - Fblx*Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]] + 
      Fblx*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
      Fmlx*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] - 
      kml*Ls*mA*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + kml*Ls*mb*Pi*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]] - kt*Ls*mb*Pi*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      kt*Ls*mb*tA*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] - kml*Ls*mb*bla[t]*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]] - Fbly*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] - 
      Fmly*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      kml*Ls*mb*mla[t]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + kt*Ls*mb*mla[t]*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]] + kt*Ls*mb*mra[t]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] - 
      kml*Lt*mA*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] - kml*Lt*mA*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]] + kml*Lt*mb*Pi*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      kml*Lt*mm*Pi*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] - kml*Lt*mb*bla[t]*Sin[mla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]] - kml*Lt*mm*bla[t]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      Fbly*Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      Fbly*Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      kml*Lt*mb*mla[t]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + kml*Lt*mm*mla[t]*Sin[mla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]] - Fmlx*Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      Fblx*Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 - Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]*
       Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 - Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[mla[t]]*
       Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + 
      Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*
       Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + 
      Ls^2*Lt*mb*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - 
      Ls^2*Lt*mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*
       Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*

      Ls^2*Lt*mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*
       Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls^2*Lt*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*
       Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - 
      Ls^2*Lt*mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*
       Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]*
       Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2*
       Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - 
      Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*
       Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 -

       Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + 
      Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]*
       Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]^2*
       Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[mla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
      Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]^2*
       Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]*
       Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
      Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]^2*
       Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt^2*mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
       Sin[mra[t]]^2*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt^2*mb^2*Cos[bla[t]]*
       Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]^2*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 -

       Derivative[1][mra][t]^2)/(Ls^2*Lt*mb*(mb + mm)*
      (Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]] - Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
      (Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bra[t]] - Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))) - 
   ((-(Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]) - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*

             Sin[mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
            Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
            Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
           Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
           Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
           Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
           Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2))*(-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) -

             Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
           (-(Fbly*Ls*Cos[bla[t]]) - kml*(-mA + Pi - bla[t] + mla[t]) - 
            Fblx*Ls*Sin[bla[t]] + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + Ls*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][
              t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
              Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Ls*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - 
              Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*

                t]) - (mb*(2*Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]*

                   Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][

         (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*

           kml*(-mA + Pi - bla[t] + mla[t]) - kt*(Pi - tA - mla[t] - 
             mra[t]) - Fblx*Lt*Sin[mla[t]] - Fmlx*Lt*Sin[mla[t]] -

           Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
           Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
           Lt*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*
            (Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*
              Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) + 
           Lt*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]*
            (-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
             Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
            Derivative[1][mla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
             Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
              Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
             t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - 
             Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) -

                  Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][

                  Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
                  t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                  t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2))) + 
      (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*

           Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
          (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
            Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
          Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*
         (-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
           Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
          Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
       (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
            Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
           Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*
            Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
          (-(Fbly*Ls*Cos[bla[t]]) - kml*(-mA + Pi - bla[t] + mla[t]) -

            Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*

            Derivative[1][bla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - 
             Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*

                  t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*

                t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*

          Fty*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] - kt*(Pi - tA - mla[t] - mra[t]) + 
          kmr*(-mA + Pi - bra[t] + mra[t]) - Fblx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] - 
          Fmlx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] - Ftx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*
           Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*
           Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
           Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
           Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*
           Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
           Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Lt*mt*Sin[mra[t]]*
           Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] + 
            Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Sin[mra[t]]*
           Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
            Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
           (-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
            Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
            Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
           Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
            Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
           (-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - 
            Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
          (mt*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][bra][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
                 t]) - 2*Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
              (-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
          (mm*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                 t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
             2*Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                 t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
          (mb*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
                 t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
               t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                 t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2))))/
    (Ls*(Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bra[t]] - Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
     ((-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
            Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
           Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
          (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
            Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
          Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*
         (-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
           Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
          Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
       (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
            Sin[mla[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
           Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
            Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
           Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
            Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
          Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*
         (-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
           Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
          Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) - 
      (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
            Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
           Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
            Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])) + 
        (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
           Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + 
          Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]^2))*
       (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
            Sin[mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
           Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
            Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
           Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
            Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
          Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
          Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
          Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
          Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2)))) + 
   ((mm*mt*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mb*mt*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2 - 
      2*mb*mt*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
      mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      mm^2*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      mb*mt*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      mb*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      mm^2*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + 
      2*mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      2*mm^2*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      2*mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      2*mm^2*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
      mb*mm*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mm^2*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mb*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mm^2*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mb*mt*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Cos[mla[t]]^2*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 - 
      2*mb*mt*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mb*mt*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Cos[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
      mm*mt*Sin[bla[t]]^2*Sin[mla[t]]^2*Sin[mra[t]]^2)*
     (((-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
         (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
            Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*
           (-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
            Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) - 
        (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]^2))*
         (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) +

            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2)))*
       ((-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
         (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 +

             2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
            (-(Fbly*Ls*Cos[bla[t]]) - kml*(-mA + Pi - bla[t] + mla[t]) - 
             Fblx*Ls*Sin[bla[t]] + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*

            Fmly*Ls*Cos[bra[t]] + Fmry*Ls*Cos[bra[t]] + Fty*Ls*Cos[bra[t]] - 
            kmr*(-mA + Pi - bra[t] + mra[t]) - Fblx*Ls*Sin[bra[t]] - 
            Fmlx*Ls*Sin[bra[t]] - Fmrx*Ls*Sin[bra[t]] - Ftx*Ls*Sin[bra[t]] + 
            Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + 
            Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + 
            Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + 
            Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 +

            Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 + 
            Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 - 
            Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 - 
            Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]^2 -

             (Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*

              t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*
               Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
                t]) - Ls*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]*
             (-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
              Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Ls*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
              Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Ls*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][bra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) -

               Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Ls*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
              t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - 
              Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) -

                  Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
            (mm*(-2*Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*

                   t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Ls*
                Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*

                   Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*
                 Derivative[1][bla][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][
                     t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
                  Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2)) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(Fbly*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] + Fmly*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] + 
            Fty*Lt*Cos[mra[t]] - kt*(Pi - tA - mla[t] - mra[t]) + 
            kmr*(-mA + Pi - bra[t] + mra[t]) - Fblx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] - 
            Fmlx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] - Ftx*Lt*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 - Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t]^2 - Lt*mt*Sin[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] + 
              Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Sin[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t] - 
              Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
              t]*(-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] + 
              Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mt*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
              Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mm*Cos[mra[t]]*
             Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - 
              Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][mra][t]) - Lt*mb*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
              t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
               Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - 
              Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 
            (mt*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][bra][t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][
                   t]) - 2*Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
                (-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
            (mm*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                   t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*
                Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][bra][t]) - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                   t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2 - 
            (mb*(-2*Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*
                (-(Ls*Cos[bla[t]]*Derivative[1][bla][t]) + Ls*Cos[bra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][bra][t] - Lt*Cos[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][
                   t] + Lt*Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]) - 2*Lt*
                Cos[mra[t]]*Derivative[1][mra][t]*(-(Ls*Sin[bla[t]]*
                   Derivative[1][bla][t]) - Ls*Sin[bra[t]]*Derivative[1][bra][
                   t] - Lt*Sin[mla[t]]*Derivative[1][mla][t] - Lt*Sin[mra[t]]*
                  Derivative[1][mra][t])))/2)))))/
    ((mb + mm)*mt*(Cos[mla[t]]*Sin[bla[t]] - Cos[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
     (Cos[mra[t]]*Sin[bra[t]] - Cos[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
     (Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] - Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])*
     (-((-((-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
                Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*
                Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
               Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])) + 
            (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + 
              Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]^2))*
           (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*
                Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*
                Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
              (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
                Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
              Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[
                bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
              Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]]))) + (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*
               Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^
                2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
             (Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mla[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[
                mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]]))*(-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
              Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[
                mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*
             (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])))*(((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]) - 
           (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*
            (Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
          (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[
                mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[
                bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + 
              Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
           (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
             Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) - 
         ((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]) - (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]))*
          (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[
                bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
              Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
           (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
             Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2)))) + 
      (-(((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]) - (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]]))*
          (-((Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 
              Ls^2*mt*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + 
              2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2)*
             (-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[
                mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
             Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))) + 
        ((-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])^2 - (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]^2)*
           (Ls^2*mb*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 2*Ls^2*mm*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + 
            Ls^2*mt*Cos[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + 
            2*Ls^2*mm*Sin[bra[t]]^2 + Ls^2*mt*Sin[bra[t]]^2))*
         (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])))*
       ((-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[
                mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*
             Sin[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]]))*
         (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
            Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*
           (-(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) - Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]*
             Cos[mra[t]] + Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
            Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]*Sin[mra[t]])) - 
        (-((Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]])*(-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]]) - 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mla[t]] + Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mla[t]])) + 
          (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
             Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Cos[mla[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mb*Sin[mla[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mla[t]]^2))*
         (-((-(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[mra[t]]) + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])*(Ls*Lt*mb*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Cos[bra[t]]*Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Cos[bra[t]]*
              Cos[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mb*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + 
             Ls*Lt*mm*Sin[bra[t]]*Sin[mra[t]] + Ls*Lt*mt*Sin[bra[t]]*
              Sin[mra[t]])) + (-(Ls^2*mb*Cos[bla[t]]*Cos[bra[t]]) + 
            Ls^2*mb*Sin[bla[t]]*Sin[bra[t]])*(Lt^2*mb*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mm*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mt*Cos[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mb*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + Lt^2*mm*Sin[mra[t]]^2 + 
            Lt^2*mt*Sin[mra[t]]^2)))))}]
